KitKat::

She looked at Blackfang, "Join me in the mess hall. We have much to 
discuss."  She turned and followed Cooley. She stopped and patted Cam 
on the head. "Nice to see you again little one. I must admit, you are 
a sight for sore optics."  She went with Cooley.
 "Sir, you gave me a hose to complete me? I don't understand. But if 
it would please you, I have something that may earn my place at your 
side."
She stopped and opened her chest plate. She revealed one of the 5 
HOLDERS OF THE MATRIX.  She pulled it out and handed it to 
Cooley. "Perhaps it will aid you, my lord." She smiled as she handed 
it to him. She hoped he would be please by it.
